## 신규 약물 기준 재구성 (2026-05-07 cycle 110)

본 NANOBOT axis 의 main work scope 가 hexa-bio 의 신규 약물 (de novo drug) lifecycle 안에서 representative role 로 reframe. 기존 F-NB-* falsifier (single molecular nano-machine actuation + inter-rater audit) 는 axis canonical 보존; novel drug precision-delivery context 의 representative falsifier path 추가.

cross-link:
- `.roadmap.novel_drugs` — de novo drug list (initial 5 hxq-* candidates)
- `.roadmap.fda_drug_verification` — verification phase historical
- `.roadmap.meta_novel_drugs` — 5-axis representative + 6-stage lifecycle (§1.5 NANOBOT)
- `.roadmap.disease_{cancer,alopecia,mi,lung_normalization}` — disease-specific Phase α-δ

### Novel drug contribution (NANOBOT axis)

- **novel nanobot precision delivery** — microneedle (alopecia topical) / aerosol (lung) / liposome (systemic)
- **disease-microenvironment-responsive release** — pH (tumor 6.5 vs healthy 7.4) / ROS / protease / temperature
- **inter-rater audit** — novel nanobot design 의 robustness (F-NB-1, F-NB-2 cycle 19-29)
- **molecular nano-machine actuation** — drug payload + trigger mechanism + release kinetics

### Representative falsifier (novel drug 기준)

| ID                  | scope (novel drug context)                                |
|---------------------|----------------------------------------------------------|
| F-novel-ca-NB-N     | TME-responsive (pH/ROS) drug release for hxq-ca-*         |
| F-novel-al-NB-N     | microneedle / topical follicle-localized for hxq-al-*     |
| F-novel-mi-NB-N     | clot-targeted thrombolytic + ROS-responsive for hxq-mi-*  |
| F-novel-ln-NB-N     | inhaled aerosol nanoparticle alveolar deposition for hxq-ln-* |
| F-novel-NB-cross-N  | per-novel-drug 5-axis Stage 3 delivery + Stage 4 release  |

### Phase plan (novel drug 기준)

- Phase α: each disease 의 hxq-* 의 nanobot encapsulation modality 결정
- Phase β: disease-microenvironment trigger 검증 (in vitro mock)
- Phase γ: targeted release + drug payload activation
- Phase δ: cross-axis Stage 3 — hxq-* + NANOBOT delivery + 다른 axis (WEAVE scaffold / VIROCAPSID capsid) 결합
